snippet.title: Heroes of Might and Magic 3 Armageddon's Blade Intro
snippet.description:
Intro movie for Heroes of Might and Magic 3 Armageddon's Blade.

Game was developed by New World Computing and published by 3DO. Games' musics are composed and created by Paul Anthony Romero and Rob King
